In the MATTER OF the ADOPTION OF A CHILD BY R.C.W. and S.M.W. (G.R. - Petitioner) C-574 September Term 2018
081807 Supreme Court of New Jersey. February 8, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002907-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
